Invocation Name: running tips
des:
Everyone can run, but there are bits of info to improve your efficiency and just make running more fun. Here is an opportunity to get tips and keep your running joyful.

Note: The information in this skill is provided for informational and educational purposes only. It is not a substitute for professional medical advice, treatment or diagnosis. It is always best to seek out the advice of a medical professional such as a doctor or licensed physical therapist. If you think you may have a medical emergency, please dial your local emergency response phone number.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
